question: What will be the NS Discord member count on January 1, 2026 at 3 PM UTC?
description: Predict the total member count of the NS Discord server on January 1, 2026 at 3 PM UTC. Trading closes on December 31st at 11 PM UTC. The member count will be determined by the visible server statistics at the exact resolution time.
resolutionCriteria:
This market resolves based on the NS Discord server's total member count at exactly 15:00:00 UTC (3 PM UTC) on January 1, 2026.

Resolution process:
Member count will be determined from the Discord server statistics visible at the resolution time
The count includes all members (active and inactive) as shown in the server's member list
A screenshot of the server statistics will be taken at the exact resolution time for verification
If the member count falls outside the market range (2,000-2,200), the market will resolve to the nearest boundary bucket
Market Initial Range: 2,000 - 2,200 members
